results.name: Energy
results.description: Companies engaged in exploration, production, refining, marketing, storage and transportation of oil, gas, coal and consumable fuels.

results.name: Materials
results.description: Companies involved in the discovery, development, and processing of raw materials including mining, chemicals, construction materials, metal, paper, and forest products.

results.name: Industrials
results.description: Companies that produce capital goods, provide commercial services and transportation services including aerospace, defense, machinery, construction, and engineering.

results.name: Consumer Discretionary
results.description: Companies that provide non-essential goods and services including automobiles, durables, apparel, hotels, restaurants, leisure, media, and retailing.

results.name: Consumer Staples
results.description: Companies providing essential consumer goods including food, beverages, tobacco, and household products.

results.name: Health Care
results.description: Companies in healthcare equipment, services, pharmaceuticals, biotechnology, and life sciences sectors.

results.name: Financials
results.description: Companies involved in banking, diversified financials, insurance, and real estate, including REITs.

results.name: Information Technology
results.description: Companies providing technology software, hardware, semiconductors, communications equipment, and IT services.

results.name: Communication Services
results.description: Companies providing telecommunications, media, and entertainment services including wireless, internet, publishing, advertising, broadcasting, and social media.

results.name: Utilities
results.description: Companies providing electric, gas, water utilities, and independent power producers and energy traders.

results.name: Real Estate
results.description: Real estate companies and REITs that own, develop, and manage properties, facilities, and infrastructure.
